301
00:48:11,202 --> 00:48:11,652
“Why?”

302
00:48:11,652 --> 00:48:14,371
“Because, You know my husband doesn’t
give me any money.”

303
00:48:14,371 --> 00:48:18,871
I said, “Give him up. I don’t mind. He
must give you money. Why doesn’t he give

304
00:48:18,871 --> 00:48:19,772
you money?”

