00:49:31,222 --> 00:49:37,452
you must tell them, it’s your duty. They
were not born out of the trees but they were

316
00:49:37,452 --> 00:49:43,242
born here, from the parents. So it’s the
duty of the parents to tell them that this

317
00:49:43,242 --> 00:49:49,462
is wrong and this should not be done. It’s
a very wrong thing, you should correct them

318
00:49:49,462 --> 00:49:54,121
and that correction should be in a Sahaj way.

319
00:49:54,121 --> 00:50:08,046
I’ll tell you an example. I had a problem
