00:50:20,115 --> 00:50:25,506
is a funny caricature, you know, I can’t
think of a Sahaja Yogi smoking. How will I

323
00:50:25,506 --> 00:50:27,615
look if I start smoking like that?”

324
00:50:27,615 --> 00:50:30,420
“Ah, horrible.”

325
00:50:30,445 --> 00:50:36,896
I said, “Then if you are My son, you cannot
smoke, it looks bad.” He gave up smoking,

326
00:50:36,921 --> 00:50:38,920
can you imagine?

327
00:50:39,161 --> 00:50:47,155
So, dealing with children, always make yourself
an example, yourself part and parcel of that

328
00:50:47,180 --> 00:50:59,776
event. So the children don’t feel, you know.
This is something that I have talked many

329
00:50:59,801 --> 00:51:07,885
a times. Children is one thing, I tell you,
they can give up everything but not your love.

330
00:51:07,910 --> 00:51:18,691
If they know you love them they will not accept
anything that will make you not love - not

331
00:51:19,159 --> 00:51:28,515
love them. This is for definite, because children
