00:52:43,376 --> 00:52:45,687
“Is it, you like it?”

344
00:52:45,712 --> 00:52:46,743
“Of course!”

345
00:52:46,768 --> 00:52:48,227
“More than chocolate?”

346
00:52:48,252 --> 00:52:49,651
“Of course!”

347
00:52:50,644 --> 00:52:55,045
I was surprised. “What? You eat them or
